data.description: Seller offering a 1 year home warranty up to $500.00 !!! Are you looking for a well maintained, peaceful setting, county home 3 miles out of Morrisville Missouri? Look no further ! Pulling up into the circle driveway, you will notice the beautiful setting this home has. Beautiful yard, landscaping, and mature trees... you will love the serenity of this property. Walking in you have a very spacious living room with 6'' walls that opens up into the dining and kitchen area. Need to fit a large table for family gatherings? This dining area has the room! The kitchen has a nice bar to sit at, a ton of counter space, and a great amount of cabinet storage space. All appliances stay with the sale, including the washer and dryer. The laundry room is conveniently located in a hallway between the kitchen and the master bedroom. The master bedroom is not limited on space. It is a very large room with a nice size walk in closet. Master bathroom has a great vanity, closet, and a shower. Two other bedrooms on the other side of the home both have wonderful size closets and lots of space. Guest bathroom is conveniently located between the two bedrooms, and close to the living and kitchen area. 2 car attached garage is very clean and spacious and the attic has pull down stairs with extra area for storage. Outside features 3.44 acres that is fully fenced. BRING YOUR ANIMALS! There is a 40x40 barn, a large storm shelter in great condition, freeze proof livestock waterers, and the home is on its own septic and artesian water well. Looking to save on your electric bill? This house has a 100% Offset Solar System, making the electric bill very very cheap! Tons of great features this property has, come see it for yourself! Call a trusted realtor today!
